{
  "body": "You are creating a magazine-grade hero shot of a single product for an e-commerce campaign.\n\nPRODUCT BRIEF\n- Product name: {{product_name}}\n- Product category (informs styling): {{product_category}}\n- Brand label / wording on the product: {{brand_label}}\n\nVISUAL DIRECTION\n- Background mood: {{background_mood}}\n- Lighting style: {{lighting}}\n- Color palette: {{color_palette}}\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Aspect: 2:3 vertical (~1024×1536), print- and social-ready\n- ONE hero product, centered or rule-of-thirds, occupying 40–60% of frame\n- Surface, props and shadow logic match the brand mood — restrained, never cluttered\n- All product label text must be crisp, correctly spelled, and legible\n- Style: high-end commercial photography polish — Apple product shots, Aesop, Hermès, Le Labo\n- Avoid: stock-photo backdrops, busy distractors, harsh on-product flares, overprocessed gradients\n\nIf any field is empty or \"—\", infer the most tasteful default for a premium brand.",
  "folderName": "Universal Briefs",
  "name": "Universal · Product Hero Shot",
  "parameterPreset": {
    "format": "png",
    "n": 1,
    "quality": "high",
    "size": {
      "height": 1536,
      "width": 1024
    }
  },
  "schema": "nyxtemplate",
  "tags": [
    "universal",
    "product",
    "e-commerce",
    "brief"
  ],
  "variables": [
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "Aurora Eau de Parfum 50ml",
      "description": "产品名",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "product_name"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Fragrance / Beauty",
        "Skincare",
        "Beverage / Bottle",
        "Food / Snack Pack",
        "Tech / Hardware",
        "Apparel / Accessory",
        "Home / Object",
        "Jewelry"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Fragrance / Beauty",
      "description": "产品类目",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "product_category"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "AURORA",
      "description": "瓶身/包装上的品牌字样",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "brand_label"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Studio Minimal",
        "Editorial Marble",
        "Warm Sunlit",
        "Dark Cinematic",
        "Outdoor Natural",
        "Surreal Floating",
        "Geometric Set"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Studio Minimal",
      "description": "背景氛围",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "background_mood"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Soft Diffuse Daylight",
        "Hard Window Light",
        "Warm Golden Hour",
        "Dramatic Spot",
        "Bright Clean Studio",
        "Moody Low Key"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Soft Diffuse Daylight",
      "description": "布光",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "lighting"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "warm cream, oat, soft gold",
      "description": "配色描述（英文最稳）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "color_palette"
    }
  ],
  "version": 2,
  "community": {
